headline: The Trade Desk (TTD) Soars 6.6%: Is Further Upside Left in the Stock?
summary: The Trade Desk (TTD) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock doesn't suggest further strength down the road.

headline: The Trade Desk Stock Climbs Higher on S&P 500 Debut as ANSYS Drops Out
summary: TTD jumps 6.6% as it joins the S&P 500. The company expects CTV growth, Kokai demand and global ad trends to fuel momentum.
